{"tid":1423140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家會不會換件返紅衫同揮香港旗？","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T13:22:32.000Z","uid":295632,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fd5250308fecf6ee91e3ae1d58a8d900ea03f448","tid":1423140,"uid":295632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:59:47.000Z","msg":"紅色說明大家的憤怒又好，拉攏返中間派d 派D 市民支持又好<br />\n見你地成日著黑衫，叫黑警，叫黑社會。<br />\n証明你地熱愛香港，爭取雙普選。"},{"pid":"a02837c92dfd96b18feec514758916cd43e5793d","tid":1423140,"uid":209679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd5250308fecf6ee91e3ae1d58a8d900ea03f448","tid":1423140,"uid":295632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:59:47.000Z","msg":"紅色說明大家的憤怒又好，拉攏返中間派d 派D 市民支持又好<br />\n見你地成日著黑衫，叫黑警，叫黑社會。<br />\n証明你地熱愛香港，爭取雙普選。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:00:24.000Z","msg":"紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143fda0c2633f5f6383f99f8b58caed3eb781ee7","tid":1423140,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:00:37.000Z","msg":"雙普選ok, 抽氣扇不了"},{"pid":"f3ada32ae179bb7f6b2ba269c2f86576fbfc5a12","tid":1423140,"uid":202137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:01:20.000Z","msg":"著彩虹色呀笨"},{"pid":"de228e3a96e1a05f7f544572c9645a1b34e951a4","tid":1423140,"uid":137,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:01:31.000Z","msg":"紅色代表奶共好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a2ed8971ae3a95e1b37e74ba2c9a938438e3d3","tid":1423140,"uid":133519,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:03:43.000Z","msg":"有人話五大訴求先係初心，叫人唔好再衝擊，唔好搞警察，要對準政權。<br />\n<br />\n情況就好似有人將你鎖咗喺間屋入面，再放火燒屋。<br />\n<br />\n人地擺明想燒死你，你就不斷求佢俾鎖匙。<br />\n<br />\n我打算撞爆度門逃生，你就同我話勿忘訴求，鎖匙先係重點，唔好失焦。<br />\n<br />\n你仲期望個殺手會放過你？我跳窗都要搏下啦！<br />\n<br />\n宜家香港人聽到革命，獨立就驚，話會得罪中共，又話香港無本錢。<br />\n<br />\n乜大家唔係想出老解咩？咁點解又怕得罪中共？<br />\n<br />\n你哋究竟知唔知自己做緊乜？<br />\n<br />\n你哋口口聲聲話要民主同自由，但係又唔敢抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n唔敢諗獨立，唔通你哋其實想感化共產黨？<br />\n<br />\n建設民主中國仲難過搞港獨喎，香港人係咪仲要等中共施捨「民主」俾你？<br />\n<br />\n你班左膠咁驚港獨，俾林鄭月娥話你港獨，你地就自我審查，要改口號。<br />\n<br />\n咁不如由政府搞標語創作大賽，再等市民投稿俾政府，最後由林鄭選出勝利者好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n其實，香港仲有險可守咩？"},{"pid":"3f73e3dae927504530f0ec270e0782754a806850","tid":1423140,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8B%B1%E5%B1%AC%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF#/media/File%3AFlag_of_Hong_Kong_(1959%E2%80%931997).svg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%23%2Fmedia%2FFile%253AFlag_of_Hong_Kong_%281959%25E2%2580%25931997%29.svg&h=fe785772&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港旗"},{"pid":"02dd4680eaf33f189d3232b822db8096b8faab7d","tid":1423140,"uid":56015,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3f73e3dae927504530f0ec270e0782754a806850","tid":1423140,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8B%B1%E5%B1%AC%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF#/media/File%3AFlag_of_Hong_Kong_(1959%E2%80%931997).svg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%23%2Fmedia%2FFile%253AFlag_of_Hong_Kong_%281959%25E2%2580%25931997%29.svg&h=fe785772&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港旗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/51/Flag_of_Hong_Kong_%281959%E2%80%931997%29.svg/1280px-Flag_of_Hong_Kong_%281959%E2%80%931997%29.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuploa